<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>The Spot Smoke Shop | El Paso, TX</title>
  <meta name="description" content="El Paso's favorite spot for premium vapes, THCA, glass, merch & more. Open 24/7 at multiple locations. Delivery coming soon!"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f0f0f;
      --accent: #00ff9d;     /* neon green vibe */
      --accent-dark: #00cc7a;
      --text: #e0e0e0;
      --card: #1a1a1a;
    }
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #000, var(--bg));
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,157,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #bbb;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .status {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(0,255,157,0.15);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
      margin: 1rem 0;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0,255,157,0.4); }
      70%     { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,157,0); }
    }
    .coming-soon {
      background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.15);
      color: #ffc107;
      border: 2px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    section {
      margin: 3rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .locations {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .location-card {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .location-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,255,157,0.15);
    }
    .location-card h3 {
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    footer {
      background: #000;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      border-top: 2px solid #333;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #888;
    }
    .social-links a {
      color: var(--accent);
      margin: 0 1rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
      .status { font-size: 1.3rem; padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>THE SPOT</h1>
    <p class="tagline">El Paso's Favorite Puff Stop</p>
    <div class="status">OPEN 24/7</div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section>
      <h2>Premium Products • 5-Star Vibes</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
        Vapes • THCA • Glass • Edibles • Concentrates • Merch & More<br>
        Imported top-shelf products • Best prices in the 915
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="coming-soon">
      🚀 <strong>Delivery Coming Soon!</strong> 🚀<br>
      Get your favorites delivered straight to your door — stay tuned!
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Locations</h2>
      <div class="locations">
        <div class="location-card">
          <h3>Pebble Hills</h3>
          <p>14087 Pebble Hills Blvd, Ste 106<br>El Paso, TX 79938</p>
        </div>
        <div class="location-card">
          <h3>Dyer St</h3>
          <p>9740 Dyer St #107<br>El Paso, TX 79924</p>
        </div>
        <div class="location-card">
          <h3>Zaragoza</h3>
          <p>1641 N Zaragoza Rd<br>El Paso, TX 79936</p>
        </div>
        <div class="location-card">
          <h3>Kenazo / Horizon City</h3>
          <p>494 N Kenazo Ave<br>El Paso, TX 79928</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Follow Us</h2>
      <p class="social-links">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/thespotsmoke915" target="_blank">@thespotsmoke915</a> •
        <a href="https://x.com/thespotep" target="_blank">@thespotep</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 The Spot Smoke Shop • El Paso, Texas • 21+ ID required • Support Local 915</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
